\section Intro Introduction

libgfsmxl is an abstract C library for online lookup operations
in cascaded finite state automata.

\section building Building libgfsmxl

Run the \a configure script in the distribution directory, and then call \a make:

\verbatim
bash$ cd gfsmxl-XX.YY.ZZ

bash$ ./configure
